Testing Different Request On Petstore Application

Update the newly created Pet and verify the pet name and status has updated

Scenario Outline

When Pick up newly created petname <name>,update name to <updatedname> and status to <status> check
Then I verify the pet is updated using name <updatedname> and status <status>

Examples: 

# Name Status Updatedname
1 pretty available pretty_doggie
  Steps Outcome
Example: {name=pretty, status=available, updatedname=pretty_doggie}
SUCCESS 3.55s
When Pick up newly created petname pretty,update name to pretty_doggie and status to available check
SUCCESS 2.58s
Getting the pet information using the petId:pretty
SUCCESS 1.04s
GET https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/pet/findByStatus?status=available
